efficient subcounter use:
	Na uparxei se kathe slave ena eidos id monitor to opoio kathe fora pou ginetai deallocation na upologizei tin nea timi tou id (an auto ginetai)

	provlimata sxetika me auto:
		pws tha kseroun to size tou counter pou ginetai deallocate 
		pws tha ananewnw egw to mask se kathe deallocate symfwna me ta nea id

	gia to update tis mask: maskref, shift tin mask >>size kai meta or me tin ref mask i kati tetoio
	alla o slave tha prepei na exei kati san id monitor opote otan to id einai megalytero apo auto tou deallocate na kanei id-size 


stroba signal gia ta load data wste na dinetai i dynatotita na alazei sygkekrimena bytes stous subcounter tou enas counter